Package: which-terminal
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: x-terminal-emulator
Description: Universal terminal emulator launcher
 which-terminal is a tool that detects and runs the best available terminal
 emulator on your system. It prioritizes terminals based on the display server
 (X11 or Wayland) and running processes.
 .
 This package provides both the which-terminal binary and an x-terminal-emulator
 symlink for compatibility with Debian's alternatives system.
